definitions.definition: The act of creating pages for a document, book, etc., or determining when to truncate text on the pages.
The act of numbering pages for a document, book, etc.
The separation of data into batches , so that it can be retrieved with a number of smaller requests .

main_definition: The act of creating pages for a document, book, etc., or determining when to truncate text on the pages.
secondary_definitions: The act of numbering pages for a document, book, etc.
( computing ) The separation of data into batches , so that it can be retrieved with a number of smaller requests .
